      "comment": "ZIPPER SURPRISE (2) got around 400m in a respectable 22.86 when winning a Grade 5 at this track last start. Has the ability and looks hard to top. GARY INDIANA (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (23.33) in a Grade 5 at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Shapes as one to consider. SPARKLING WHEELS (5) missed the frame latest (23.72) when seventh over 400m at this track in a Grade 5. Already a winner from this draw. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. RHONDA FULL DAY (1) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
